_sText:
Here is my second Jailbreak map

Jail Up

Introduces New Types Of Cells

Cells: 12 cells that are lowered into the ground when the button is pressed the cells rise out of the ground.

VIP: TV w/ "moving picture", couch, plants, laser/fog switch

Pool: Very Deep Pool W/ Shower Room including steam

Last Request Room: Enough Room To Do Shot For Shot, Platform For Deagle Toss, enough room for race

Armory: Stocked Full Of fully armed weapons. Almost every weapon avalible is in armory

Infirmary: Just Walk In No Button To Press

Small Soccer Field: Behind Infirmary

Hidden Areas: There Are A Few Hidden Areas For The T's To Find
